{"tid":681485,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學潛水小心NAUI旗下Viva Diving HK","createTime":"2018-05-28T05:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T12:48:53.000Z","uid":188314,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"72452bae6b7f108100915894a5a4d553755d51e4","tid":681485,"uid":188314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T05:45:55.000Z","msg":"懶人包：<br />\nNAUI課程總監林汝聰，教練及VIVA金主阮國禧，教練羅敏枝，三人隱瞞學生，用無牌教練去教授，同時沒有提供足夠氧氣的樽給學生訓練。經常有學生出事，但還好沒搞出人命。但以他們經營手法，再沒有人阻止是遲早事。<br />\n<br />\n本人在2016年報了Viva Diving HK 潛水教練課程，報名時說好4-5人一班，但後來改了13人一班，說好17年4月考完試就會出牌。<br />\n<br />\n完了考試又被要求幫手實習，實習目的是要我們13人去帶班，但13人沒有資格去教授，而且又沒有學習過教授技巧，但負責人只說，想要教練牌就要照著做，而且我們下海，必須要1支氣樽，最少潛2次，或半支潛一次。我們有人試過不夠氣，要跟學生輪流用。經常有學生退出或者受傷，甚至有人要追討。<br />\n<br />\n到了2017年尾，實習完了，又被迫參加外潛當畢業旅行。之後又改期到2018年，我EMAIL去NAUI總部查詢教練情況，得知沒有教練課程資料，其後VIVA被我揭穿真相，更把本人踢出VIVA會，亦向其他人表明課程還沒有完成，更表明部分人不及格，最後導致13人，只如下4人留底。<br />\n<br />\n本人已向小額錢債申索，其他人也在準備中，在庭上VIVA負責人辯護，稱收取學費只用在書本與租用場地費用，并不涉及教練費，VIVA教練都是提供義務教學。當然法官最後不接納這說法。<br />\n<br />\n依家收到風，佢地打算唔玩NAUI，轉會去SDI。<br />\n<br />\n而審訊日期會在2018年7月30及31日，香港小額錢債審裁處進行。<br />\n<br />\n我們不是第一界被欺騙，在過去教練班VIVA都是用這種手法經營，只是大家怕事，一直沒有人舉報，所以VIVA可以一直逃之夭夭，希望大家可以廣傳，杜絕這個潛水家的害蟲。<br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">認人唔好認會</span>，因為佢地會轉會同改公司名，打算東山再起<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/133258_99ba0d493bd13c30c24b3d77ae7f423c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F133258_99ba0d493bd13c30c24b3d77ae7f423c.png&h=da1d16a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/133310_c7b6093903d766dd29adbc498fd9a822.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F133310_c7b6093903d766dd29adbc498fd9a822.png&h=57e6238f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/133321_88c8c7e6dc5e1dea50c71b968a3dc82f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F133321_88c8c7e6dc5e1dea50c71b968a3dc82f.png&h=8b1ecd66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無牌教學，教到學生受傷資料<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/133520_555c24b43923986e691ec84a0e4d59f8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F133520_555c24b43923986e691ec84a0e4d59f8.png&h=af1a8248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/133534_9405efab09ab86869e0b4d3440a0b4f6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F133534_9405efab09ab86869e0b4d3440a0b4f6.png&h=f0be8f5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/133542_fa5c56b0995a8a7370b9fb25c6c17733.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F133542_fa5c56b0995a8a7370b9fb25c6c17733.png&h=446640df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依個學生醒，知唔對路就無玩<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/133728_a3be0865b1839117ba6f4b3664f53200.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F133728_a3be0865b1839117ba6f4b3664f53200.png&h=04afeaf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢口中阿靈同阿駿都唔係教練，阿駿就係我。<br />\n<br />\n上庭日期，有時間黎聽<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/134002_cb849c845a810845e10cd8f0ceaa4b9d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F134002_cb849c845a810845e10cd8f0ceaa4b9d.jpeg&h=c53d4d09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nVIVA個FB，好耐無更新<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vivadiving/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvivadiving%2F&d=jVfVKlZMpNPP2cvnjC5RPgHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=4b5f637c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/vivadiving/</a><br />\n<br />\n我個FB專業，有最新消息及更多資料，幫手廣傳<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vivadivingswindler/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvivadivingswindler%2F&d=jVfVKlZMpNPP2cvnjC5RPgHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=3bc27376\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/vivadivingswindler/</a>"},{"pid":"e6981ec552fe6a024b65dd931144286a404bd470","tid":681485,"uid":20624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T05:48:02.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"3487377fbc5f48733480adf10dafb27d429d5874","tid":681485,"uid":87043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T05:48:23.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"e21b157650abe6175688e3692d50a7314ca1a47a","tid":681485,"uid":188314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T06:40:12.000Z","msg":"詳盡資料：<br />\n首先講起原本2017年完左水季阮國禧就會出牌俾所有人，但條件要去畢業旅行，本身傾好2017年11月去，阮國禧話要齊11個學生夾到時間先去。<br />\n<br />\n我之後就揾課程總監林汝聰，了解情況，但對方就已讀不回，打電話又揾唔到佢。我就EMAIL去NAUI問我教練班進度，對方就話無任何資料，我同其他同學既教練班根本沒開始過，香港代表更將我嘅查詢轉告俾VIVA，隨即阮國禧就話我唔合格。<br />\n<br />\n我係高登發POST，表示係VIAV學潛水俾人呃。係我不斷在網上制造輿論時，其他同學就把握時機拿我做籌碼去同阮國禧傾，同學答應阮國禧要求，影張證書相放上高登將件事降溫，換取DM證書。但事後佢地發現證書過期或者無教練簽名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/142336_002bccc8c9e85ffbdd08d47413bd8d7a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F142336_002bccc8c9e85ffbdd08d47413bd8d7a.png&h=35678cba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/142557_ebd24a5f52b18b2a1f2daac87cc27c49.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F142557_ebd24a5f52b18b2a1f2daac87cc27c49.png&h=16621493&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/142608_7838423e7420e27a3cc0a4923aaed127.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F142608_7838423e7420e27a3cc0a4923aaed127.png&h=8fcc01b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係我被人踢走後林汝聰，阮國禧就向留底同學表明仲有課程同考試，更表明有同學未達標。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/28/C3KuoO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2FC3KuoO.png&h=1219d464&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/28/6pnSI9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F6pnSI9.png&h=dc634dcf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/28/QsoXNr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2FQsoXNr.png&h=f185d47c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/28/rXz1pu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2FrXz1pu.png&h=88f7d9db&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/28/M0o2lm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2FM0o2lm.png&h=579cb346&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n部分同學覺得唔對路，擔心又要幫手實習多年，而所謂實習沒教練，沒野學。只係搬野，煮飯，洗碗，洗廁所，洗船。仲要單獨帶班教學（無牌教學）。更離譜係我地要一支氣樽最少潛兩次，或者得一半氣或者更少進行教班，有同學試過用到無氣要和學生輪流用。所以經常有學生潛到出事。<br />\n <br />\n最後5位同學退出左VIVA潛水會<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/28/et5fCh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2Fet5fCh.png&h=b2c247d5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/28/Sy84Pl.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2FSy84Pl.png&h=ec831ff5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/28/purx04.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2Fpurx04.png&h=8dfcbadd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最初13個學生，用左2年時間，做左成年免費勞工，由一開始識到做朋友，一齊做功課，一齊去潛水，到最後日日玩無間道，直到反面，最後得返4個合格，1個退左錢，其他上庭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/28/j2YagJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2Fj2YagJ.jpg&h=eb2d21ec&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/28/2PfY53.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F2PfY53.png&h=2e5da124&s={SIZE}\" />[/quote]"},{"pid":"ff8d1b903fca0e0b72316588309e7880f8308e14","tid":681485,"uid":188314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:19:08.000Z","msg":"再續：<br />\n因我地揚左件事又退學追究，導致肥仔佢地冇得用以往手法去搵教練班學生幫手無牌帶班，原本今年諗住搵左班之前係VIVA教出黎既教練，以合作形式幫手開班，但因我又再發POST，令到部分人表明退出。<br />\n<br />\n我提醒任何打算同VIVA 潛水會 或者阮國禧，林汝聰，羅敏枝 合作或幫佢地。個VIVA會係羅繁枝註冊，你地幫完成季水，佢一清盤，阮國禧一蚊都唔洗賠俾你地。我收到風，VIVA今年沒學生打算賣船，但無人要，最後加燈改造墨魚船，之前係VIVA有個以合作形式教左成年，又合作賣裝備既女MISS，已經一早走左人拆伙，你地唔好做水魚。<br />\n<br />\n免得俾人話我亂講，之前VIVA幫女MISS宣傳資料，聽聞佢退出左就唔好打擾到佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/29/emkslH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2FemkslH.png&h=d5f9d8fa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n羅繁枝公司查冊<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/29/eJ63Uo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2FeJ63Uo.jpg&h=987c68d6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/29/VYPS9r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2FVYPS9r.jpg&h=6d26d87a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/29/1NZybQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F1NZybQ.jpg&h=5b08718c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/29/WKNwfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2FWKNwfb.jpg&h=3bf58177&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/29/JRorXd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2FJRorXd.jpg&h=d8c8192a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/29/gvmurC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2FgvmurC.jpg&h=697113ec&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/29/NhaTBJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2FNhaTBJ.jpg&h=23484dc3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/29/8XE1dr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F8XE1dr.jpg&h=8b38581e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n查冊顯示，阮國禧只係VIVA秘書，所以你地同佢合作，諗清楚佢出蠱惑，你地點追究。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/29/b9PFES.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2Fb9PFES.jpg&h=60782b6e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/29/7lC5gy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F7lC5gy.jpg&h=3edecafa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/29/iyVe0q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2FiyVe0q.jpg&h=fa6ab21c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"617ea161349ac8bf3ee59f9f83308231caaf0629","tid":681485,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51161d79d6496ddefb319670bc7822ef7f36f54a","tid":681485,"uid":59895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:08:33.000Z","msg":"我17年經呢間野學潛水，<br />\n咁咪即係無論係理論定實習都係呢班所謂&ldquo;教練&rdquo;去教<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166f9fb2a949718bdeed5c2460c29da16d268cb7","tid":681485,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8522dd7d4af427521ba88755b3a47a1b705227b4","tid":681485,"uid":188314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T15:13:05.000Z","msg":"再續：<br />\n據我所知及見過北葵拯溺女負責人係跳池同羅繁枝談及租借事宜，而羅敏枝係北葵拯溺會成員之一，所以我相信，VIVA透過羅繁枝關係向北葵拯溺會租借跳池進行潛水訓練，簡單講就係北葵拯溺會租完個跳池就轉租俾VIVA賺錢。同時牽涉北葵拯溺會違反可以優先租用條件，一定要進行拯溺相關課程。係依事揚左之後，北葵拯溺會負責人李國泉係今年5月已經無再租跳池俾VIVA，VIVA轉用摩士公園游泳池。<br />\n<br />\n聽閒摩士公園游泳池非由潛水總會申請租借，而是由羅敏以枝救生員關係租到，同時由於VIVA本身沒咩學生，所以佢地再轉租俾其他潛水會。<br />\n<br />\n羅敏枝本身係康文署救生員，佢開公司冇利益申報，我已經舉報，但康文署過左回履限期，都沒回到我，我已經EMAIL去申訴專員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/230746_a23a26dcd94f53924751aca3fb58e62f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F230746_a23a26dcd94f53924751aca3fb58e62f.png&h=b6d12e8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/230834_7351c72a82da3d447d1c6885956770b2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F230834_7351c72a82da3d447d1c6885956770b2.png&h=8b0972ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/231025_7e1d662b90ce002d30e396f7bbffdc61.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F231025_7e1d662b90ce002d30e396f7bbffdc61.png&h=40722474&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/231209_9613c6388b9609b4eb2e171b0c4bd35d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F231209_9613c6388b9609b4eb2e171b0c4bd35d.png&h=060992d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33849d0a9e89b6d3f385565a317da87cf7f8a1b9","tid":681485,"uid":188314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51161d79d6496ddefb319670bc7822ef7f36f54a","tid":681485,"uid":59895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor